---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Case Study: How Spotlight Dance Academy Achieved 82% Re-enrollment | Lead Flow North" description="A Mississauga dance studio transformed their seasonal operations with marketing automation.">
  <article class="py-12 md:py-20">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <!-- Back Link -->
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto mb-8">
        <a href="/industries/fitness-gyms/dance-studios" class="inline-flex items-center text-sky-600 hover:text-sky-700 dark:text-sky-300 font-medium">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 19l-7-7 7-7"></path></svg>
          Back to Dance Studios
        </a>
      </div>
      
      <header class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center mb-12">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-4 mb-6">
          <span class="bg-green-100 dark:bg-green-900/30 text-green-700 dark:text-green-300 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-medium">Case Study</span>
          <span class="text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 text-sm">5 min read</span>
        </div>
        <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-6">
          How Spotlight Dance Academy Achieved 82% Re-enrollment
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300 mb-8">
          A Mississauga dance studio transformed their seasonal operations with marketing automation.
        </p>
      </header>

      <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto mb-12">
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-pink-600 to-purple-600 rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-12 text-white">
          <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-2">82%</div>
              <div class="text-pink-100">Re-enrollment</div>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-2">97%</div>
              <div class="text-pink-100">Recital Attendance</div>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-2">41%</div>
              <div class="text-pink-100">Multi-class</div>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-2">3.2x</div>
              <div class="text-pink-100">Costume Revenue</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <div class="prose prose-lg prose-slate dark:prose-invert max-w-none">

          <div class="bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-800 p-6 rounded-xl my-8 not-prose">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-4">Client Overview</h3>
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 text-sm">
              <div>
                <span class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300">Business:</span>
                <span class="font-medium text-slate-900 dark:text-white ml-2">Spotlight Dance Academy</span>
              </div>
              <div>
                <span class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300">Location:</span>
                <span class="font-medium text-slate-900 dark:text-white ml-2">Mississauga, ON</span>
              </div>
              <div>
                <span class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300">Type:</span>
                <span class="font-medium text-slate-900 dark:text-white ml-2">Full-service dance studio</span>
              </div>
              <div>
                <span class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300">Styles:</span>
                <span class="font-medium text-slate-900 dark:text-white ml-2">Ballet, jazz, hip hop, tap, contemporary</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mt-12 mb-4">The Challenge</h2>

          <p>
            Lisa Chen's studio had amazing instructors but chaotic operations. Fall enrollment was overwhelming. Recital deadlines were missed. Dancers took one class when they could take more. Summer saw major drop-off.
          </p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mt-12 mb-4">The Solution</h2>

          <p>We implemented early re-enrollment campaigns, recital management automation with costume and rehearsal reminders, multi-class promotion sequences, summer camp campaigns, and systematic parent communication.</p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mt-12 mb-4">The Results</h2>

          <p>Re-enrollment hit 82%. Recital attendance reached 97%. Multi-class enrollment jumped to 41%. Costume and merchandise revenue tripled. Seasons now run smoothly with minimal stress.</p>

          <blockquote class="border-l-4 border-pink-500 pl-6 my-8">
            <p class="text-xl text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 italic mb-4">
              "Recital season used to be pure chaos. Now everything is automated—costume reminders, rehearsal schedules, ticket sales. Parents know exactly what to do. We can focus on the dancing, not the logistics."
            </p>
            <cite class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300 not-italic">— Lisa Chen, Owner</cite>
          </blockquote>

          <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-pink-600 to-purple-600 p-8 rounded-xl text-white my-12">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-white">Ready to Grow Your Studio?</h3>
            <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 text-pink-600 px-6 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-800 transition">
              Book Your Free Demo
            </a>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </article>
</Layout>
